assault weapons already barred from import into the united states 
and outlaw clips of more than 15 bullets 
bidens bill also would create an independent organized crime 
and dangerous drug division in the justice department this would 
effectively overturn a decision by attorney general dick thornburgh 
that gave local us attorneys control over the departments 
vaunted organized crime strike forces 
