a foreign exchange there are a whole host of problems and anything 
can happen 
but there is a pervasive sense among some scholars that 
communism has been exposed as a failed experiment 
i think the idea that you can run a society or an economy 
effectively by centrally placed authoritarian or dictatorial means 
has been proven bankrupt shultz said 
