the french socialist party congress ended 
in failure sunday with the struggle for the leadership unresolved 
and the party unable to agree on a basic political program 
the power struggle between major personalities that has rent the 
party in recent months went down to the wire and allnight attempts 
to work out a compromise in committee ultimately failed 
