continentals concourse one of three planned at the new airport 
closer to its ticket counter under the new plan all of 
continentals gates are attached to the terminal building instead 
of being in an outlying concourse 
denver plans to begin selling up to 800 million in bonds next 
month to finance the initial phase of airport construction 
