equalize perpupil expenditures between poor and rich school 
districts free teachers and schools from rote manuals to instruct 
in accord with local needs reward successful schools with bonus 
money to spend as they see fit except for athletics 
best is an allout drive for school betterment all the more 
remarkable for a state that didnt used to have compulsory 
