blacks 
the impetus for reform is simple economics to be ignorant in a 
computer world is to be eyeless in gaza 
at every level of planning for our future higher employment 
higher standards the basic need was always education says olon 
ray mabus special assistant for education and a former teacher 
our chance for improvement in the state in the united states 
lies in our human capital 
more than a tenth of americans cant read or write says the 
us census lack of a high school educated work force costs the 
nation an estimated 225 billion yearly 
mabus aims to cut the dropout rate twice the nations average 
in half by the year 2001 and reduce illiteracy by 90 percent a 
sobering fact is that threequarters of mississippis projected 
work force in 2001 is already beyond school age 
theyre all were going to get and we need more brains than 
brawn says mike zitterman manager for fritolays mississippi 
operation as a result fritolay has donated a semitruck equipped 
with 10 computers to travel the state teaching basic skills to 
adults 
for a change mississippi has a first in the nation a 25 
percent tax credit for corporations that teach adult education 
packard electric in clinton is spending 300000 a year to teach 
its workers there are almost 50 adult literacy programs in the 
state with 40000 enrollees says judy lipscomb director of the 
governors office for literacy 
mabus is impaled on the horns of a selfmade dilemma he says he 
takes a dim view of raising taxes to pay for his ambitious 
best his predecessor william winter bit a similar bullet 
among the memorabilila and diplomas on the wall of winters 
jackson law office is a painting of a oneroom country school i 
was the only student from that school ever to graduate from high 
school he says winters mother was the teacher more than 
cat she taught her son a respect for education 
in 1952 one in four whites in mississippi finished high 
school one in 40 blacks did he says 
to change this dismal record winter ran for governor in 1967 on 
an education reform platform and lost ditto in 1975 he ran a 
third time in 1979 and won 
