casualties with amputated legs the first time she made her rounds 
that she had to leave the emergency room i had never seen 
anything quite like that she would say 
but the most difficult part of her tour was when a youngster 
would ask her how do i write and tell my wife i dont have a leg 
anymore 
nurse sharon lanes medical battalion treated 10000 patients in 
