disillusionment set in during the late 1960s and early 1970s 
in 1961 tom davis wrote his father i just hope that our 
little bit will help to ease things in this part of the world i 
dont feel too badly about having to be here when i think of all 
the potential good it will have for this country 
three days before his first christmas away from his wife and 
