massachusetts below every other state in the nation last year sampp 
reaffirmed its bbb rating last week 
bond ratings give investors a quick reference to determine the 
degree of risk on an investment the lower the rating the higher 
the risk involved 
a low bond rating means the state may have to pay higher 
interest rates on the money it borrows 
